channel.title: [317] how to make a runescape private server V2! [317] - teh war of noobs
channel.description:
hey everybody i just finished typing this out! this is on how to make a runescape private server (note): this is only for 317 servers! so if you dont want to code a 317 server i recommend that you do [size=36pt]NOT[/size] download this! [size=18pt]this package i typed out includes:[/size] ~ Setting up no-ip ~ portforwarding ~ Setting up JDK ~ Coding the Blank Source ~ Adding shops ~ Adding NPC's ~ Adding Object's ~ Changing price of items ~ Changing Stats of Items ~ A crap load of tools! ~ A good Tutorial ~ A Blank Client and Source! ~ Item ID lists ~ Object ID Lists ~ NPC ID lists
(note): not all of this was done to me, i have to give credits to some guys thing i downloaded for all these extra tools you might need along the way: ~"ZodiacsReigonPackage" ~ http://www.google.ca/ ~ http://www.wikipedia.com/ ~ http://www.youtube.com/
[size=36pt]- Teh war of noobs[/size]
DOWNLOAD LINK: http://uppit.com/v/B6O3G9FR http://www.megaupload.com/?d=N5RV7ILN
